{"tid":1637054,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"《孤星淚》導演撐港人抗爭 「有時暴力是別無選擇」","createTime":"2019-10-08T01:17:35.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-26T04:41:48.000Z","uid":68738,"like":73,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"c1d60ccaba4e9e1ce15c1c75df8d2551578f2345","tid":1637054,"uid":68738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T01:17:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20191007/large/1570448134_7baa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20191007%2Flarge%2F1570448134_7baa.jpg&h=44cb1573&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n《孤星淚》（Les Miserables）導演萊奇里（左）(互聯網)<br />\n<br />\n第72屆康城影展電影、講述2005年法國騷亂的《孤星淚》（Les Miserables）導演萊奇里（Ladj Ly），周一發聲支持香港的民主示威者，指如果政府「沒有做好自己的工作」，民眾上街示威是很正常，並指「有時暴力是別無選擇」。<br />\n<br />\n萊奇里周一出席第24屆釜山國際電影節說：「我只能夠支持他們。如果政府沒有做好自己的工作，民眾上街示威是很正常的。」萊奇里又以法國「黃背心」示威為例，強調自己雖然不接受或支持暴力，但有時暴力是別無選擇。<br />\n<br />\n香港示威者在示威現場唱出百老匯音樂劇《孤星淚》（Les Miserables）插曲《Do You Hear the People Sing》，憑歌寄意，爭取自由控訴霸權。《Do You Hear the People Sing》填詞人克西茨默（Herbert Kretzmer）曾在6月撰文表示：「當我在西倫敦的家看電視見到他們時，我感到喉嚨一陣哽咽。不只是因為我欣賞他們反抗中共的勇氣&hellip;&hellip;而是因為他們所唱的詞，是我在33年前寫下的，而我知道這首歌在中國被禁。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20191007/60127427?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191007%2F60127427%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&d=nKAZF5zAPcG2WvBXR7hnIiUaeeTarj8%2BpjPG%2B7PQGFg%3D&h=303d9fd2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191007%2F60127427%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&h=bf616e77\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20191007/60127427?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post</a>"},{"pid":"7e133b94d242d7778f1fc44947989f63466d90e1","tid":1637054,"uid":322141,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T01:19:38.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3093334733968573911f30b6dd97952cef53c275","tid":1637054,"uid":33077,"like":18,"dislike":1,"score":17,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T02:07:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LM49Wid.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLM49Wid.jpg&h=7ff25fbc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/ladjLY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FladjLY&d=nKAZF5zAPcG2WvBXR7hnIiUaeeTarj8%2BpjPG%2B7PQGFg%3D&h=b4cf4051\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/ladjLY</a><br />\n<br />\n好多人多謝佢<br />\n<br />\n一個外國導演都可以講出咁既說話<br />\n點解我地香港既藝人大部份都係眼裡只有錢?<br />\n唔緊要 希望你地會肯接受更多資訊而再去選擇"},{"pid":"b3f125a9b2dea915b0a0c22829133ec77a872de7","tid":1637054,"uid":40763,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3093334733968573911f30b6dd97952cef53c275","tid":1637054,"uid":33077,"like":18,"dislike":1,"score":17,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T02:07:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LM49Wid.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLM49Wid.jpg&h=7ff25fbc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/ladjLY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FladjLY&d=nKAZF5zAPcG2WvBXR7hnIiUaeeTarj8%2BpjPG%2B7PQGFg%3D&h=b4cf4051\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/ladjLY</a><br />\n<br />\n好多人多謝佢<br />\n<br />\n一個外國導演都可以講出咁既說話<br />\n點解我地香港既藝人大部份都係眼裡只有錢?<br />\n唔緊要 希望你地會肯接受更多資訊而再去選擇"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T02:22:23.000Z","msg":"唔好話香港藝人 香港人三罷都搞唔成<br />\n仲點要求藝人發聲呀<br />\n唔奶都偷笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/norma